<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>While some celebrities are taking to the beach or their boats to celebrate the Labor Day holiday, Gavin Rossdale is spending the day on the tennis court.</p>

<p>The 54-year-old Bush singer was spotted going shirtless while practicing his tennis stroke on a court in Malibu on Monday afternoon.</p>

<p>The frontman was practicing under the tutelage of the celebrity tennis coach known simply as Coach Patrick. </p>

<p>Tennis practice: While some celebrities are taking to the beach or their boats to celebrate the Labor Day holiday, Gavin Rossdale is spending the day on the tennis court</p>

<p>Rossdale rocked a neon green Nike headband while playing tennis shirtless in camo shorts.</p>

<p>He also wore brown sunglasses with two black necklaces around his neck as he practiced his game with Coach Patrick.</p>

<p>The singer completed his look with multi-colored Nike tennis shoes and royal blue socks as he showed off his toned frame on the court.</p>

<p>Gavin's look: Rossdale rocked a neon green Nike headband while playing tennis shirtless in camo shorts</p>

<p>Rossdale made headlines last month when he was seen stepping out with a mystery blonde at an outdoor market in Malibu.</p>

<p>He was spotted with his arm around the young blonde at the Trancas Country Market in Malibu on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The singer was seen taking his beloved Pomeranian pooch Chewy for a walk as they strolled through the market. </p>

<p>Gavin and Chewy: The singer was seen taking his beloved Pomeranian pooch Chewy for a walk as they strolled through the market</p>

<p>Rossdale was married to No Doubt singer Gwen Stefani from 2002 until their split in 2015, and they share three sons together, Kingston, Zuma and Apollo. </p>

<p>The singer was dating Sophia Thomalla from 2017 to 2018 and he was seeing Natalie Golba last year. </p>

<p>He recently released his band Bush's eighth studio album, The Kingdom, which debut in July but was originally supposed to be released last fall. </p>

<p>Exes: Rossdale was married to No Doubt singer Gwen Stefani from 2002 until their split in 2015, and they share three sons together, Kingston, Zuma and Apollo</p>

<p>New album: He recently released his band Bush's eighth studio album, The Kingdom, which debut in July but was originally supposed to be released last fall</p>

<p>Rossdale wrote all 14 songs on the album himself, which peaked at 14 on the Billboard 200 album charts.</p>

<p>The band is set to embark on an Australian tour in 2021, which kicks off February 16 at FBF Stadium in Perth.</p>

<p>The 13-performance tour wraps up July 5 at the Download Festival in Donnington.</p>

